data.description: AMD Ryzen 3 4100 Processor has 4 processor cores, 8 threads, and an astonishingly efficient 45-65W TDP. This processor stands with a Base Clock of 3.8GHz and a Maximum Boost Clock of 4.0GHz. It has 256KB L1 Cache. 2MB L2 Cache, 4MB L3 Cache with AM4 Package, and TSMC 7nm FinFET CMOS. This AMD processor is built with PCIe 3.0 x8 and Wraith Spire Thermal Solution. This Processor provides DDR4 Up to 3200MHz memory with 2 memory channels.

keyFeatures.value: 1 x PCI Express x16 slot, running at x16
